title: New traffic signal at Rose Avenue and Richter Street (City of Kelowna)
text: ( Source : City of Kelowna ) On Friday, Oct. 9, a new traffic signal will be activated at the intersection of Rose Avenue and Richter Street . Drivers are asked to use caution and watch for the new operation of the new traffic light. Final
